# dquants per-account deployment list  (template — copy to deployment_accounts.txt)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# One MT5 account per line, used by scripts/make_account_releases.sh to build
# one account-locked EA per line.
#
# Format:   <AccountID>  <ServerName>                  (whitespace, no expiry)
#      or:  <AccountID>, <ServerName>, <Expiry>        (comma, per-line expiry)
#   - AccountID  : the MT5 login number (digits only)
#   - ServerName : the MT5 trade-server name exactly as shown in MT5
#                  (Tools > Options > Server, or the login dialog). Optional —
#                  leave it off to lock the login on ANY server. A login number
#                  is only unique within a server, so include it when you can.
#   - Expiry     : OPTIONAL access end date. YYYY.MM.DD (valid through the END of
#                  that day) or 'YYYY.MM.DD HH:MM:SS'. Enforced on broker SERVER
#                  time (cannot be bypassed by changing the PC clock). On expiry:
#                  EAs stop opening NEW trades (open positions stay managed) and
#                  the indicator stops ALL calculation — both Alert "Expired
#                  Access". Per-line expiry REQUIRES the comma form. A blank
#                  expiry falls back to the script's --expiry default (if any).
#   - separator  : whitespace OR comma. With an expiry you MUST use commas.
#   - blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
# The real file (deployment_accounts.txt) is gitignored — it holds live account
# numbers. You can also keep per-strategy lists that are auto-detected:
#   scripts/deployment_accounts.KK-KenKem.txt
#   scripts/deployment_accounts.KK-MasterVP.txt
#   scripts/deployment_accounts.KK-MasterVP-Profiler.txt   (the indicator)
#
# Examples:
12345678   FundedNext-Server                  # locked to this server, no expiry
87654321   Exness-MT5Real8                     # no expiry
22223333,  ICMarketsSC-MT5,  2026.12.31        # expires end of 2026.12.31
44445555,  ,                 2026.09.30        # any server, expires 2026.09.30
11112222                                        # any server, no expiry
